# Out-of-tree CMake build directory.
#
# Keep this directory in git empty (only this file).  Generate artifacts
# locally with:
#   cmake -B build ...
#   cmake --build build -j$(nproc)
#
# Do not rsync or copy build/ from another host — CMakeCache.txt embeds
# absolute paths and will fail on a different machine or checkout path.
*
!.gitignore
